NEW! Our Heirloom Tomato 🍅 Panzanella Salad 🥗 is a sweet sister to your fav Caprese salad! Think: extra-crunchy croutons 🥖, ripe heirloom tomatoes, basil 🌱, & our cashew ricotta 🧀 with a simple vinaigrette dressing...need we say more? 🤩 Just 30 MINUTES to prep this EPIC summer side or lunch!⁠ // LINK in bio for the recipe!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
